Package: AskOllama
Title: A Streamlined Interface to Query Ollama's Chat Completion API
Version: 2.0.032025
Authors@R: c(
    person("Eduardo", "Tamaki", email = "eduardo@tamaki.ai", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: AskOllama provides a versatile R interface for interacting with Ollama's 
    Chat Completion API. It supports single-turn, few-shot, and multi-turn conversational
    prompts, and can seamlessly incorporate web-based research to enrich prompt context.
    Users can adjust various parameters to fine-tune response generation for a wide range 
    of applications.
